categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: This Jedi was a Human female who served the Jedi Order during the beginning of the Clone Wars. She was one of the 200 Jedi that accompanied Mace Windu to Geonosis and stage a rescue mission to free Padmé Amidala, Anakin Skywalker, and Obi-Wan Kenobi from imprisonment by the Separatists. Wielding a blue lightsaber, she fought beside Joclad Danva and destroyed numerous battle droids. It is unlikely she left the arena alive.
